    <item>
      <title>硅谷重量级人物支持卡马拉·哈里斯竞选特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/silicon-valley-heavyweights-back-harris-to-counter-gop-uptick</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，超过 200 名风险投资家公开支持卡马拉·哈里斯竞选总统，他们表示，如果没有“强大、值得信赖的机构”，硅谷和其他行业将会崩溃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/silicon-valley-heavyweights-back-harris-to-counter-gop-uptick</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 20:43:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥商人因谴责日益严重的暴力事件被杀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/mexico-businessman-killed-a-day-after-decrying-growing-violence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[边境城市塔毛利帕斯州新拉雷多的当地商会负责人在谴责该地区日益严重的暴力事件后于周二被谋杀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/mexico-businessman-killed-a-day-after-decrying-growing-violence</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:34:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
