      <title>《纽约时报》称伊朗领导人下令对以色列进行报复性打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/iran-s-leader-orders-retaliatory-strike-on-israel-nyt-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《纽约时报》报道，伊朗领导人阿亚图拉阿里哈梅内伊下令对以色列进行直接打击，以报复哈马斯最高领导人在德黑兰遇刺事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/iran-s-leader-orders-retaliatory-strike-on-israel-nyt-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:30:49 GMT</pubDate>
